title: 225: 10 Takeaways from Week 8
itunes:title: 225: 10 Takeaways from Week 8
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down all the biggest games from week 8 by giving you their ten biggest takeaways. The guys recap the quarterback duel between Watson and Wilson (4:23), the Saints gritty defensive performance (9:03), Zeke's impressive outing versus the Redskins (27:21) and much, much more.
